				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<div class="elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix"><p>Today, in my first blog post ever, I want to talk about Substance Alchemist. It is a new tool, and over the course of the last days I heard a lot about it, worked with it myself and thought about what it can provide to indie and student game developers.</p><p>If you do not want to read the website, but rather a nicely formatted pdf, or have to go offline in a bit, you can download one<span style="color: #00ccff;"> <a style="color: #00ccff;" href="https://lucahohmann.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Art-01-Substance-Alchemist-A-Real-game-changer.pdf">here</a></span>.</p></div>
