				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-c64773e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="c64773e" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<div class="elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix"><p>Substance Alchemist (SA) is a material generation tool by Allegorithmic, which currently is in its<br />open beta phase. It offers the possibility to generate materials from images, mix existing materials, and<br />apply all sorts of effects and variations onto said materials.</p></div>
